# ADR 0001: Project Conventions

## Status

Accepted

## Context

This project was generated from the `<%= template %>` template with `create-x-app`.

## Decision

- Keep project-specific conventions in `AGENTS.md`.
- Keep team coding rules in `coding-rules.md`.
- Record meaningful architecture decisions under `docs/adr/`.
- Validate behavior with package scripts before merging changes.

## Consequences

- Contributors have a stable place to find engineering expectations.
- AI coding tools can use the same repository-local context as human contributors.
